description:
On September 12, @rektober (https://x.com/rektober) challenged Mitch (https://x.com/idrawline) to a 0X.Fun PNL trading challenge (see: https://x.com/rektober/status/1834098351744102695).

This market will resolve to "Mitch" if Mitch has a greater PNL on 0X.Fun than Rektober as of 12:00 PM ET (noon) on September 30, 2024.

This market will resolve to "Rektober" if Rektober has a greater PNL on 0X.Fun than Mitch as of 12:00 PM ET (noon) on September 30, 2024.

If the PNL of each trader is exactly equal as of the resolution date or if no winner can be determined by November 7, 2024, 11:59 PM ET this market will resolve 50-50.

The resolutions source for this market will be the 0X.Fun PNL tracker (https://ox.fun/en) however a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
